data.description: This one won't last long! Full brick home located in the Tall Trees Subdivision. 2450 sq ft home on 9+ acres with full finished walkout basement, triple filtration water system, huge garage, double carport, extra large covered/uncovered deck, circular drive with gorgeous entrance gates, beautiful fountain in the front yard, hot tub (negotiable), 10,000 watt stereo system outdoors, and a bar downstairs in the basement. Newer roof, newer water heater, New HVAC. Outdoor storage building with power.  The perfect home for entertaining!  NO HOA!!!!  Very Motivated seller!  Home is occupied and some photos are virtually staged
